snippet.title: Best VGM 2288 - Phoenix Wright : Trials and Tribulations - Reminiscing ~ The Bitter Taste of Truth
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2062 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oseD00muRc8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Phoenix Wright Ace Attorney: Trials and Tribulations (2004)
Reminiscing ~ The Bitter Taste of Truth
Noriyuki Iwadare
